text.section:
Payments by the State under this subtitle may not exceed:
$250,000 to each community college campus;
$1,250,000 each to the University of Maryland, College Park, the University of Maryland, Baltimore, and the University of Maryland Baltimore County;
$1,500,000 each to Bowie State University, Coppin State University, Morgan State University, and University of Maryland Eastern Shore; and
$750,000 to each other eligible institution.
